{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "02", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "17", "M": "57", "S": "53"}}, "news": [{"title": "Adani Properties highest bidder for MHADA\u2019s Worli, Bandra redevelopment projects", "para": "Adani Properties has emerged as the highest bidder for MHADA\u2019s cluster redevelopment projects at Adarsh Nagar in Worli and Bandra Reclamation, while a consortium comprising Hanura Realty, Chandak Realtors, Premsagar Infra Realty and Vantier Realty has emerged as the highest bidder for the S.V.P. Nagar project in Andheri West.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/adani-properties-wins-major-bids-for-mumbais-redevelopment-projects/131465387?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-71380/131465387.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft in next three years", "para": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft of warehousing and industrial real estate in the next three years, nearly doubling its current operational footprint. The company is expanding into adjacent segments like in-city distribution and retail, with key projects including a large FTWZ development at Nhava Sheva and logistics parks in Pune and Bengaluru.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/welspun-one-to-lease-over-10-million-sq-ft-of-warehousing-space-in-major-expansion/131467517?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-105440/131467517.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "NGT sets up panel to probe \u2018illegal brick kiln, clay mining in Balasore", "para": "The National Green Tribunal has ordered a joint investigation into allegations of illegal brick kiln operations and unauthorized brick clay mining in Balasore district. A multi-agency p